Class Memo<T>

java.lang.Object
cs2030s.fp.Lazy<T>
cs2030s.fp.Memo<T>
Type Parameters:
T - The type of the value to be stored in Memo
All Implemented Interfaces:
Immutatorable<T>
public class Memo<T> extends Lazy<T>
Memo Class that is able to lazily compute and cache result of computation such that it does not have to be computed again. CS2030S Lab6 AY22/23 Semester 1
